title: Test
labels: A few times a month or less
summary: This grouped bar chart has 4 categories of Response on the x axis representing 3 groups: Never, A few times a month or less, and 2-3 times per week or more.
Averaging these 3 groups, the highest category is found for Response Tablet with a mean value of 33.33.
Followed by Laptop notebook or Chromebook with a mean value of 33.33.
The lowest category is observed at Smartphone that has a mean value of 33.0

In case of Hybrid or 2 in 1 computer, Never shows more dominance than any other Response with a value 84.0 and it has the lowest value 17.0 in Laptop notebook or Chromebook.  However, A few times a month or less is the second impactful group, and it has the highest value 61.0 for Response Laptop notebook or Chromebook and the lowest 10.0 in case of Hybrid or 2 in 1 computer.
